 generate responses but is not persisted on our servers beyond the active session.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium text-white/70 mb-1\",\"children\":\"Memory facts\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"missiAI extracts key facts from your conversations (preferences, habits, context) and stores them in Cloudflare KV tied to your account. These memories power the personalized experience.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"font-medium text-white/70 mb-1\",\"children\":\"Account information\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"children\":\"We use Clerk for authentication. Clerk collects your email address and basic profile information when you sign up. We do not store passwords — Clerk handles authentication securely.\"}]]}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-medium tracking-tight mb-4 text-white\",\"data-testid\":\"privacy-section-data-usage\",\"children\":\"How we use your data\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\"},\"children\":[\"Your data is used exclusively to provide AI responses and memory features within missiAI. We do not sell, share, or monetize your personal data. We do not use your conversations to train AI models. Your data exists to make missi work better for\",\" \",[\"$\",\"em\",null,{\"children\":\"you\"}],\" — nothing else.\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-lg font-medium tracking-tight mb-4 text-white\",\"data-testid\":\"privacy-section-third-party\",\"children\":\"Third-party services\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-4\",\"style\":{\"color\":\"rgba(255,255,255,0.5)\"},\"children\":\"missiAI integrates with the following services to provide its functionality:\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-xl overflow-hidden\",\"style\":{\"border\":\"1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06)\"},\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\